                  07 / 22
                %button.credit_card_registration__content__container__box__wrap__payment-list__box__form__settings-payment-remove{type: "submit"}
                  削除する
        .credit_card_registration__content__container__box__regist
          = link_to products_path, class: "credit_card_registration__content__container__box__regist__btn" do
            %span
              支払い方法について
            %i.fas.fa-chevron-right
